{
  "1702010": {
    "name": "战国王朝 - Sengoku Dynasty",
    "steam_appid": 1702010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在曾经饱受饥荒和战争摧残的地方开启新生活、发展社区并建立属于自己的王朝。独自一人或与多人合作，探索美丽的开放世界。您需要收集资源、制作物品、打猎并建造，让村庄进入自动化生产模式，从而生存下来并不断壮大。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗与经济建设两条路线中二选一，最终成为伟大的领导者。体验大自然之美，为揭开神灵的奥秘而进行古老仪式。《战国王朝》能让您身临其境地了解中世纪日本的生活。选择不同的发展道路，成为领袖、工匠、战士或僧侣，踏上一段史诗般的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/f990e8d8ea76ac68dcc3c027b58868c6.avif?t=1769761412\" width=600 height=116 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/ec48934451e170e62a0b90b26e4f0e69.poster.avif?t=1769761412\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/ec48934451e170e62a0b90b26e4f0e69.webm?t=1769761412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/ec48934451e170e62a0b90b26e4f0e69.mp4?t=1769761412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开放世界的村庄建设者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用广阔无垠的世界。从一栋房屋开始发展，建造工坊、铁匠铺和酒馆，然后把定居点壮大为遍布山谷的多个繁荣社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为真正的大名</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >统一饱受战争蹂躏的纳塔谷吧。流浪武士与强盗部落填补了权力真空，对原本拥有和平生活的村民造成了威胁。夺回被占领的领土并修复基础设施，以便更好地探索蕴藏着大量重要资源的区域，为迎接更大的挑战做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/d3b1c0e57bec5190b15c7be2c71f83f3.avif?t=1769761412\" width=600 height=116 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/35ead7690f39d7386659d0afdf66bfc5.poster.avif?t=1769761412\" width=600 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/35ead7690f39d7386659d0afdf66bfc5.webm?t=1769761412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>从手工制作到自动化</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作工具、武器、食物或药品，同时耕种土地。然后学习如何向村民分配工作并提供工具，见证经济一飞冲天，获得海量多样化的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌握复杂的战斗系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨练战斗技巧还是制造精良武器，由您自己决定。选择您最喜欢的武器，从简单的棍棒和长矛，到精心制作的武士刀和弓。掌握了连击、冲刺、格挡和反击的技巧后，您就可以征服世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>王朝管理</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为子孙后代创造一个繁荣的王朝。您需要监督村庄不断发展壮大。通过结婚确保您的遗产可以由继任者不断传承。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/fdd34730d667845f19e86d7064d40972.avif?t=1769761412\" width=600 height=116 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/85d4346e3a97649ba857d67a03a372af.poster.avif?t=1769761412\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/85d4346e3a97649ba857d67a03a372af.webm?t=1769761412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702010/extras/85d4346e3a97649ba857d67a03a372af.mp4?t=1769761412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在单人或合作模式下游玩</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以当个独行侠，一个人开辟属于自己的道路。也可以与好友联手创建规模更大的村庄，共同分担责任和任务，收集更多资源并完成任务，齐心协力推进游戏向前发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>万物皆可自定义</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照您喜欢的方式玩转战国时代。不同游戏模式和海量设置供您选择，把游戏打造为理想模样。游戏可以做到一键建造，或者干脆禁用整个战斗系统！</p>",
